title: Antioch raises pre-seed funding to accelerate AI robotics testing
description:
Antioch says its platform allows robots to be tested in virtual environments without the expense and time of other methods.

The post Antioch raises pre-seed funding to accelerate AI robotics testing appeared first on The Robot Report.
